# Next.js & React Conventions

- Use the App Router: pages and layouts under `src/app/`.
- Use functional components and hooks; avoid class components.
- Prefer `"use client"` only where needed (interactivity, browser APIs).
- Use the `@/` import alias for project imports (e.g. `@/components/...`).
- Keep components small; extract reusable logic into custom hooks.
- Use TypeScript for all new files; avoid `any` where possible.
